              <span class="tech-badge">AWS</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Docker</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
        
        <a href="https://github.com/hhassan14/hanatext" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="project-card">
          <div class="project-card-content">
            <div class="project-header">
              <h3 class="project-title">hanatext</h3>
              <svg class="external-link-icon" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
                <path d="M14,3V5H17.59L7.76,14.83L9.17,16.24L19,6.41V10H21V3M19,19H5V5H12V3H5C3.89,3 3,3.9 3,5V19A2,2 0 0,0 5,21H19A2,2 0 0,0 21,19V12H19V19Z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="project-description">(in progress) A text editor built in C, implemented with just the standard C library and a rope for efficient data storage.</p>
            <div class="tech-stack">
              <span class="tech-badge">C</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">C++</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Data Structures</span>
              <span class="tech-badge">Bash</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>